### Welcome to the site!
If you haven't realized yet, this is the August Ghosts Programming official Repo hosting site. Have fun exploring!

## Wanna join?
Well, there's like 5 of us. So yeah. You can join. Just email the admin at [August712@agpbox.com](mailto:august712@agpbox.com) about joining.
